OL,3,CCEO of Jersey's government to stay in
OL,4,Crole until at least end of year
OL,6,FJersey's government has confirmed that
OL,7,Fits current Chief Executive Officer
OL,8,Fwill continue in his role until at
OL,9,Fleast the end of the year.
OL,11,FDr Andrew McLaughlin will start on a
OL,12,Fnew contract from 1 July 2024 with a
OL,13,Fsix-month review period.
OL,15,FPreviously, he worked for NatWest in
OL,16,FLondon, and before that, he was CEO of
OL,17,FRoyal Bank of Scotland International
OL,18,Fin Jersey.
