OL,6,FHe has lived in the island since May
OL,7,F2015 and has been a regular visitor
OL,8,Fsince 1986 when he worked as a student
OL,9,Fin the island's hospitality sector.
OL,11,FHe also has a first-class degree in
OL,12,Feconomics and politics and a PhD in
OL,13,Fpublic policy.
OL,15,FChief Minister Deputy Lyndon Farnham
OL,16,Fsaid in a statement: ''I am pleased to
OL,17,Fbe able to confirm that Andrew has
OL,18,Fagreed to continue in his role.
