OL,6,F"Since starting with the Government
OL,7,Flast September, Andrew has provided
OL,8,Fclear leadership
OL,10,Facross the public service, ensuring
OL,11,Fgood governance, sound financial
OL,12,Fcontrol, and a
OL,14,Fcollaborative approach to management.
OL,16,F"As a long-standing Jersey resident,
OL,17,Fhe also has in- depth knowledge of the
OL,18,Flocal economy and community.
