OL,3,CCEO of Jersey's government to stay in
OL,4,Crole until at least end of year
OL,6,F"Retaining Andrew as our Chief
OL,7,FExecutive Officer will provide much-
OL,8,Fneeded stability and continuity across
OL,9,Fthe public sector."
OL,11,FDr McLaughlin said: "I am delighted to
OL,12,Fhave the opportunity to extend my time
OL,13,Fas CEO. It is
OL,15,Fa privilege to do this job and I will
OL,16,Fdo all I can to help the Government
OL,17,Fdeliver the best
OL,19,Foutcomes for Islanders."
